{"tid":1063701,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係你呀陳生】寶萊塢翻拍《阿甘正傳》 印度巨星阿米爾汗擔正","createTime":"2019-03-16T03:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T15:33:28.000Z","uid":16092,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6c028805a112e59becb4a15480c190202537b52f","tid":1063701,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:38:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190315/59372543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59372543&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=a6a2b9a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190315%2F59372543&h=ee0a686c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190315/59372543</a><br />\n<br />\n湯漢斯（Tom Hanks）主演的經典荷李活電影《阿甘正傳》（Forrest Gump）自1994年上映以來，一直備受電影迷喜愛，近日有外媒報道寶萊塢（Bollywood）將翻拍印度版《阿甘正傳》，已買下前作的版權，定名《Lal Singh Chadha》。電影由曾被封「印度劉華」的阿米爾汗（Aamir Khan）擔正，是他繼《打死不離歌星夢》再跟導演Advait Chandan合作，未知戲中會否重現招牌對白，「人生就像一盒朱古力，你永遠不知道自己將吃到哪一種口味。」<br />\n<br />\n寶萊塢近年發展蓬勃，平均每年出產近2,000部電影，已超越荷李活登全球影壇之冠，當地90年代開始多次翻拍美國電影，不過並非每次都有買足版權，包括照抄《猛鬼街》（A Nightmare on Elm Street）的《Mahakaal》，另外《落水狗》（Reservior Dogs）、《沉默的羔羊》（The Silence of the Lambs）、《肥媽先生》（Mrs. Doubtfire）都曾中招。"},{"pid":"9e4e20ac89c9e2ce605a65181f68bf099a766752","tid":1063701,"uid":33104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"我想睇猛鬼街點加歌舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298a63ceeb21b326113599d02accf1ecb4767427","tid":1063701,"uid":105567,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"打死不離阿甘傳"},{"pid":"5c7c3a7978a451e4fd43